  "original_title": "\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bcd \u0b95\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b88\u0bb4\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0bcd \u0b87\u0bb3\u0bc8\u0b9e\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bca\u0bb2\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Elamite youth commits suicide due to mother's reprimand",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "In Tamil Nadu, a 22-year-old youth, Niroshan, committed suicide at the Mandapam Refugee Rehabilitation Camp next to Rameswaram.",
        "It is said that for the past few days, instead of going to work, Mandapam has been hanging out with his friends at the refugee rehabilitation camp, playing games on his cell phone.",
        "Following this, the boy's mother reportedly told her son to stop playing the game and go to work.",
        "After this, Niroshan, an Eelam Tamil who was heartbroken by his mother's reprimand, mixed the rat paste in his house with water and put it behind the house two days ago and lay down after drinking it.",
        "Niroshan, who was unconscious, was given first aid treatment at the government hospital at Mandapam camp by his friends and later admitted to Ramanathapuram Government Medical College Hospital as an inpatient by a private vehicle.",
        "Subsequently, the doctors who examined him sent him to Madurai Rajaji Government Hospital by 108 Ambulance for further treatment, where he succumbed to treatment as an inpatient.",
        "Subsequently, the police are engaged in the process of bringing the body of the deceased youth to the Mandapam Refugee Rehabilitation Camp after conducting a post-mortem examination.",
        "Also, it is noteworthy that the police have registered a case and are investigating based on the complaint filed by Priya, the sister of the deceased Eelam Tamil youth. (R)"
      ],
